narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I have become more adept at answering research-related questions. I have learned Adobe Illustrator and worked on a review article.

A lot! MRI acquisition, data processing and analysis. Improving my skills with Matlab. And, overall increasing my knowledge of literature in the field of visual perception. I also practiced preparing a manuscript for submission.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Very rigorous and engaging. The primary weakness is that nature can be unpredictable and difficult to model.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, research in the lab is always important.
